entries.journal_entry_description: Tell the Spokesperson for the disgruntled townspeople  that water is on the way and then let Nym know that the townspeople should be satisfied, now.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Go back to the Spokesperson for the Disgruntled Townspeople and let him know that clean water is on the way.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Return to The Spokesperson for the Townspeople
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Tell Nym that nothing will really make this guy happy but at least the water is fixed.
